Description

  • The size if respective to amount of data available, the scale for USGS and USACE points are different.
  • The color for the USGS points are based on the percentage of missing data:
    • "20%-100%: pink"
    • "5%-20%: orange"
    • "1%-5%: blue"
    • "0%-1%: green"
  • The color for USACE points are:
    • Red: Corresponding USGS point available
    • Black: Corresponding USGS point not available
  • The color for connections are:
    • Blue: Main Branch
    • Black: Tributories
    • Gray: Control Sources
